snippet.title: Shadow of Naught - Official Game Trailer (Landscape Mode)
snippet.description:
#PlayStore: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=studio.taawoos.shadowofnaught
#AppStore: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/shadow-of-naught/id1521652779

Shadow of Naught is an award winning game with interactive gameplay and emotive storytelling.

Awards:
🏆 Grand Prix (IMGA MENA)
🏆 Best Meaningful Play (IMGA MENA)
🏆 Excellence in Storytelling (IMGA MENA)
🏆 Best Upcoming Game (IMGA MENA)
🏆 Colossal Leap Award (ADVENTUREJAM)

Official Page: https://playplayfun.com/shadow-of-naught-an-interactive-story-adventure-game/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ShadowOfNaught/
